096                                return result;
097                        }
098                        case ContentPackage.RESOURCE: {
099                                Resource resource = (Resource)theEObject;
100                                T result = caseResource(resource);
101                                if (result == null) result = caseModelElement(resource);
102                                if (result == null) result = caseMarked(resource);

106                                return result;
107                        }
108                        case ContentPackage.TEXT: {
109                                Text text = (Text)theEObject;
110                                T result = caseText(text);
111                                if (result == null) result = caseModelElement(text);
112                                if (result == null) result = caseMarked(text);
113                                if (result == null) result = caseAdaptable(text);
114                                if (result == null) result = caseIMarked(text);
115                                if (result == null) result = defaultCase(theEObject);

121                                if (result == null) result = caseFilter(interpolator);
122                                if (result == null) result = caseModelElement(interpolator);
123                                if (result == null) result = caseMarked(interpolator);
124                                if (result == null) result = caseAdaptable(interpolator);
